  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape Haunted Mansion is a horrific multiplayer deduction game for 3 to 10 players with voice chat. The Haunteds must complete tasks to escape, while the Cursed seek to eliminate them discreetly.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape from manor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/8f80e8e77c58a17d3863b95283ab184a.avif?t=1762705618\" width=1280 height=360 /></span>You and your band of friends find yourselves trapped in the basement of a haunted mansion after an exploration gone wrong. Except one of your friends isn't, and he's the one who brought you all here, knocked you unconscious, and imprisoned and killed you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/bea02532aceec60b3faa4302937399c1.poster.avif?t=1762705618\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/bea02532aceec60b3faa4302937399c1.webm?t=1762705618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/bea02532aceec60b3faa4302937399c1.mp4?t=1762705618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete tasks to escape</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/a688d012d64c916d38596611d2790758.avif?t=1762705618\" width=1280 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get out of here and try to unmask the culprit who deceived you. Then carry out all the tasks necessary for your release. Cooperate to be more efficient in your quest for freedom. Be careful, unmasking your cursed friend won't set you free - you have to complete all the tasks necessary to win and escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/9ecff87e72d08c55f5363dd348e61a15.poster.avif?t=1762705618\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/9ecff87e72d08c55f5363dd348e61a15.webm?t=1762705618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/9ecff87e72d08c55f5363dd348e61a15.mp4?t=1762705618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If everyone dies except your cursed friend, then it's all over for you and he wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't trust anyone, be quick and complete all the tasks to get away and save yourself.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape Haunted Mansion is a horrific multiplayer deduction game for 3 to 10 players with voice chat. The Haunteds must complete tasks to escape, while the Cursed seek to eliminate them discreetly.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Escape from manor</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/8f80e8e77c58a17d3863b95283ab184a.avif?t=1762705618\" width=1280 height=360 /></span>You and your band of friends find yourselves trapped in the basement of a haunted mansion after an exploration gone wrong. Except one of your friends isn't, and he's the one who brought you all here, knocked you unconscious, and imprisoned and killed you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/bea02532aceec60b3faa4302937399c1.poster.avif?t=1762705618\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/bea02532aceec60b3faa4302937399c1.webm?t=1762705618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/bea02532aceec60b3faa4302937399c1.mp4?t=1762705618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Complete tasks to escape</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/a688d012d64c916d38596611d2790758.avif?t=1762705618\" width=1280 height=360 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get out of here and try to unmask the culprit who deceived you. Then carry out all the tasks necessary for your release. Cooperate to be more efficient in your quest for freedom. Be careful, unmasking your cursed friend won't set you free - you have to complete all the tasks necessary to win and escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/9ecff87e72d08c55f5363dd348e61a15.poster.avif?t=1762705618\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/9ecff87e72d08c55f5363dd348e61a15.webm?t=1762705618\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3542310/extras/9ecff87e72d08c55f5363dd348e61a15.mp4?t=1762705618\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If everyone dies except your cursed friend, then it's all over for you and he wins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't trust anyone, be quick and complete all the tasks to get away and save yourself.</p>",
